{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"font-family","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/font-family","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG Attribute reference home</a></p>\n<p><code>font-family</code>&nbsp;属性 (attribute) 指出哪个字体集将被用来渲染文字， 在带优先级的字体集名称列表被指定，还有或没有泛指的字符集名称。(specified as a prioritized list of font family names and/or generic family names)。</p>\n<p>作为一个表现层的属性，<code>font-family</code>属性也可以被直接用在 CSS 样式表中，详见 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/font-family\"><code>css font-family</code></a> 。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用上下文","title":"使用上下文","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">分类</th>\n   <td>Presentation attribute</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td>[[&lt;family-name&gt; | &lt;generic-family&gt;],]* [&lt;family-name&gt; | &lt;generic-family&gt;] | inherit</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可动画 Animatable</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/text.html#FontFamilyProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<h4 id=\"css\">CSS</h4>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">p.class1{font-family:\"Times New Roman\",Times,serif;}\np.class2{font-family:Arial,Helvetica;}\n</pre>\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>class1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This is a paragraph, shown in the Times New Roman font.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>class2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This is a paragraph, shown in the Arial font.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下元素可以使用<code>font-family</code>&nbsp;属性 (attribute)</p>\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#text_content_elements\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Text_content_elements\">Text content elements</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另见","title":"另见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/font-family\"><code>css font-family</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用上下文","id":"使用上下文"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"另见","id":"另见"}],"summary":"« SVG Attribute reference home","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"font-family","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/font-family","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/font-family/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/font-family","title":"font-family"}],"pageTitle":"font-family - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}